M*A*S*H Version 2
-----------------

Details of the full registered version are contained in the game documents.
The full version contains many enhancements over this version and comes on
2 disks. To order, send £ 7.00 Postal Order/ Cheque in Sterling/Punts to the
address given above. If living outside of the U.K. & Ireland just send
whatever works out handiest in your own currency ! If you have access to 
E-Mail, feel free to drop me a line before sending off your hard earned cash,
and I can answer any questions you might have. Please state your system 
setup when ordering.



